Rating: 4
I am an experienced baker, yet had never made an angle food cake. This recipe was perfect, even at high altitude (I live at 5000 feet). I followed the directions exactly, but then had an oven problem, baked the cake at 475F for only about 15 minutes and it came out great, light, fluffy and tasty. I will make this again and will cook it at the recommended temperature.

