Rating: 3
I made this cake for my wife who's dieting, and she loved the taste and the fact that is so low in calories, as it's mostly air, protein from the eggs and not too much sugar. I personally would use less cream of tartar next time as I feel it gave the cake a little overy salty-bitter taste. The mango sauce was simply delicious. It added freshness and a little zing from the ginger.

Rating: 4
I've made this numerous times, with and without the sauce, and either way it is delicious!

